Century Global Commodities Corporation 			 



 You are here:  Home   /   Social Responsibility   /  Health and Safety Health and Safety 

 Health and safety is a priority we hold above all others and we are committed to providing a  healthy and safe workplace. 
 Our Policy Includes: 

 Ensuring contractors comply with the same high standards as the Company; 
 Providing facilities, equipment, tools, procedures and health and safety training; 
 Leading employees and contractors through training and direction about workplace procedures, practices and rules; and 
 Complying with all applicable laws and regulations. 

 We will: 

 Provide adequate resources for health, safety, and environmental programs; 
 Continuously improve the effectiveness of health and safety programs; 
 Comply with appropriate legislation, regulations, standards and codes of practice; 
 Implement a health and safety management system ; 
 Manage risk by hazard identification, elimination and monitoring; 
 Ensure employees and contractors are trained to perform their duties safely; 
 Use positive reinforcement and involvement of employees and contractors in the development of health and safety procedures; and 
 Co-operate with government and local communities on health, safety to develop a positive contribution and best practice. 

